.SH "NAME"
\fBwemux\fR \- multi\-user tmux sessions made easy
.
.SH "SYNOPSIS"
Host or join multi\-user tmux sessions\.
.
.P
WEMUX HOST COMMANDS
.
.br
\fBwemux start\fR
.
.br
\fBwemux attach\fR
.
.br
