.
.br
\fBwemux config\fR
.
.br
\fBwemux help\fR
.
.br
WEMUX CLIENT COMMANDS:
.
.br
\fBwemux mirror\fR
.
.br
\fBwemux pair\fR
.
.br
\fBwemux rogue\fR
.
.br
